								<h2 style="color:white"><u>IN-GAME COSMETICS</u></h2>
								<p>info about DNC unlockable in-game cosmetics</p>
							</header>
							<p style="color:white">As of christmas 2019, DNC players will be able to unlock in-game cosmetic effects for free. </p>
							<p style="color:white">Players will be rewarded in-game cosmetics by achieving certain community support goals. (for example, creating or administrating large DNC servers, advertising DNC on youtube, etc...). To claim an in-game cosmetic reward please email us at <a>disckord35@gmail.com</a> with your <i>exact in-game username</i> and proof of your community role/achievement and your in-game cosmetic effect will activate within a couple days.</p>
							<p style="color:white">Players can also be rewarded in-game cosmetic effects when donating to DNC. (see our <a href="donate.html">donation page</a>). When donating you will be given a cosmetic effect based on your amount donated, with higher amounts being rewarded with effects such as <i>flames (includes fire sound effect), cherry blossom leafs, </i>and lower amounts being rewarded with effects such as <i>smoke, steam, bubbles(includes bubble sound effect) and lava/water drops.</i> See our <a href="donate.html">donation page</a> for a full list of obtainable cosmetic rewards at different donator ranks.</p>
							
						</div>
					</div>
