		<!-- Two -->
			<section id="three" class="wrapper style2">
				<div class="inner">
					<div class="box">
						<div class="content">
							<header class="align-center">
								<h2 style="color:white"><u>ABOUT DNC</u></h2>
								<p>Everything you need to know about dnc</p>
							</header>
							<p style="color:white">Disckords nostalgia client (DNC) was created by disckord initially as a passion project. Disckord wanted to create a client that would provide the best way to experience classic minecraft. With the look, feel and mechanics of older versions of minecraft, dnc incorporates newer features and quality of life such as sprinting, server lists, breeding, weapon/armor upgrates etc. DNC also has added features such as Ted-80's world generation, optional alpha aesthetics and optifine for 1.5.2 (shader support).</p>
						
						<p style="color:white">DNC is established to make all hack clients currently available redundant, using complex obfuscation and private source code. This means a vanilla dnc server will never need an anti-cheat plugin. Rest assured knowing you wont be x-rayed or esp'd ever again. There will not be any cheats made for DNC for a very, very long time.</p>
						
						<p style="color:white">DNC automatically updates every time you launch the game. Similarly to official versions of minecraft. The server will have to be re-downloaded every update. Players with a different version to the server will not be able to join and will be told their client or server is out of date. In the launcher you will find newest patch notes and notifications if your launcher is out of date. </p>
						
							
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
